    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The target must be a creature you are grappling with and have pinned. Make a Grapple check against the target. If successful, the target can make a Reflex save (DC 20) to avoid being 'kissed' by you. If it does not, you may use the Chakra Vampire ability to drain 1d6 Chakra, though the target can make a Fortitude save (DC 15) to resist, having you drain only 1 Chakra if successful. Cannot be used two rounds in a row.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The fifth step increases the Chakra drain to 1d8 on a successful kiss.</p>\n",
